      "date": "2014-07-17 00:55:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/cc0c4372-0d4c-11e4-8ce3-5254006e85c2).  Ran 6 tests.  No failures.",
